A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering servers glow with neon blue and magenta light, connected by streams of luminous data flowing like rivers between buildings. In the foreground, a massive translucent shield wall divides the scene—on one side, chaotic red-tinted external networks with fragmented geometric shapes trying to penetrate; on the other, a protected green-hued inner sanctum of sleek database monoliths humming with organized energy. Digital pathways snake through authentication checkpoints that pulse with verification rings. The sky is filled with holographic API endpoints floating like constellations, while the ground level shows layered security zones rendered as glowing floor tiles transitioning from crimson to emerald. Rain falls through the scene, each droplet catching the multicolored light of this technological fortress.
